AddKeysToAgent yes

Host bitbucket.org
	HostName bitbucket.org
	IdentityFile ~/.ssh-private/id_rsa

Host bitbucket.org-imt
	HostName bitbucket.org
	IdentityFile ~/.ssh-private/id_rsa_imt

Host github.com
	HostName github.com
	IdentityFile ~/.ssh-private/id_rsa

Host default
	HostName *
	IdentityFile ~/.ssh-private/id_rsa
